{"tid":853940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"淫棍伯父摸姪女胸部下體　辯稱：睇佢係咪發燒","createTime":"2018-10-09T03:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T05:05:44.000Z","uid":46896,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3f839d3ae43d47162f80c2ef09688a774e79946c","tid":853940,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:45:07.000Z","msg":"台灣新竹一名17歲少女日前熟睡期間，突被伯父撫摸胸部與下體，睜眼看見色狼竟是伯父後更嚇得尖叫連連。事件被揭發後，伯父辯稱因為姪女感冒，他才會伸手摸她的頭、手及肚，看她有沒有發燒。 <br />\n<br />\n事發於今年5月，涉案男子到弟弟家探親並暫住一晚，當晚與親姪女同睡一室，不料他竟然色心起，伸手撫摸姪女，直到姪女驚醒後他才逃離現場。姪女嚇得整晚不敢入睡，只好向同學求救，同學代為告訴老師，老師認為事態嚴重，報警並通報社工處理。 <br />\n<br />\n涉案男子被捕後供稱，當時因為姪女感冒，他只是好心幫忙照顧她，否認猥褻姪女。但是姪女同學證言，當時同學向她求救時十分害怕，加上受害人指證歷歷，新竹地檢署日前以乘機猥褻罪嫌起訴伯父，同時建議法官以兒童少年福利權益保障法加重判刑。"},{"pid":"3dedb83b15c8957d49583b0109a6400f2e370b73","tid":853940,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:51:15.000Z","msg":"中呀"},{"pid":"a7c433eb6466ff000af62db9ad24cd38531a8c4a","tid":853940,"uid":212683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:51:54.000Z","msg":"過兩日咪又係庭外和解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead36b6413f96d4d90ea97c65f2bf62e781fd25d","tid":853940,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:52:45.000Z","msg":"西熱？"},{"pid":"4415358247ac6f8528ec4aed5f101d763cdaf854","tid":853940,"uid":16070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:53:32.000Z","msg":"所"},{"pid":"fe8c89f63e33595773febba36f4eb7d59774258f","tid":853940,"uid":213709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:54:34.000Z","msg":"奶熱"},{"pid":"90aa82fcbd9de76de0cc4051c50fae50009ffca8","tid":853940,"uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:57:14.000Z","msg":"勞資糾紛"},{"pid":"5ee95b67a7535270fe8ae47727b1bcf0469c4d8a","tid":853940,"uid":215337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:59:13.000Z","msg":"唔～～唔好摸...摸我啦...我好熱啊....～"},{"pid":"73aa0479ef30d44e59e5a7c953edb8d1cd60091c","tid":853940,"uid":128741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"又係新竹市"},{"pid":"b60b96ee0e66ddc80f607d79ef008d4f32794190","tid":853940,"uid":5607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"又估中"},{"pid":"affd827e3a985771148fc8db39f745e0384e9afd","tid":853940,"uid":103513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:02:09.000Z","msg":"新竹同新北競爭好激烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f59e5a8d5affdccac9ee03cd98d2bb4c0970296","tid":853940,"uid":30090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"90aa82fcbd9de76de0cc4051c50fae50009ffca8","tid":853940,"uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:57:14.000Z","msg":"勞資糾紛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:02:19.000Z","msg":"悶唔悶"},{"pid":"440f24fcaea02510c5d596dcd2a8b5039da13494","tid":853940,"uid":86097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:05:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a8e244c8564804fb1b2a2c6c364aa37128b68af","tid":853940,"uid":33796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:05:44.000Z","msg":"當晚與親姪女同睡一室<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}